OL,4,CBA and Ryanair investigated for
OL,5,Crefusing refunds
OL,6, British Airways and Ryanair may have
OL,7, broken consumer law in not offering
OL,8, refunds to customers who couldn't
OL,9, legally take flights due to Covid
OL,10, lockdowns, a watchdog has said.
OL,12,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) said the airlines' stance could
OL,14,Fhave left customers out of pocket.
OL,16,FThe airlines offered other options, but
OL,17,Fboth refused refunds, it said.
OL,19,FHowever, BA said it had acted lawfully
OL,20,Fand Ryanair said it had refunded
OL,21,Fcustomers in justified cases.
